Fish - Fzf Shortcuts

In [prgm]fish[/prgm], use the following shortcuts to spawn an [prgm]fzf[/prgm] picker.

  [cyan]Ctrl[/cyan] + [cyan]Alt[/cyan] + [cyan]F[/cyan] (File)      - Search directory
  [cyan]Ctrl[/cyan] + [cyan]Alt[/cyan] + [cyan]L[/cyan] (Log)       - Search git log
  [cyan]Ctrl[/cyan] + [cyan]Alt[/cyan] + [cyan]S[/cyan] (Status)    - Search git status
  [cyan]Ctrl[/cyan] + [cyan]Alt[/cyan] + [cyan]H[/cyan] (History)   - Search history
  [cyan]Ctrl[/cyan] + [cyan]Alt[/cyan] + [cyan]P[/cyan] (Processes) - Search processes
  [cyan]Ctrl[/cyan] + [cyan]Alt[/cyan] + [cyan]V[/cyan] (Variables) - Search environment variables
